nodes.text: Star Wars: Return of the Jedi Tin

The Star Wars: Return of the Jedi Tin is a canon children's activity set in the Star Wars Construction Books series. It was published by Egmont UK Ltd on September 8, 2016. The set includes two young-reader books (a Return of the Jedi storybook and the Star Wars: Jedi vs. Sith Activity Book) and an All Terrain Scout Transport press-out model kit.
